We computed the effective reproduction number RE (average number of secondary cases caused by an infected individual) to evaluate an intervention’s effectiveness. We calculated an overall RE for an average individual (patients and HCWs combined) but also stratified RE by patients, HCWs and symptom status. The reproduction numbers of patients were calculated for those who eventually developed symptoms \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
